  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, DiscreteInput, Descriptive
    public class NumericPulseData
extends AbstractData
implements DiscreteInput
    An instance of the AbstractData class, which also declares an externalID. Use to store numeric data of the pulse for each measurement imported from an external source.
